EffectDescription:
Phase 1 Bond: Charge Points granted by pinging orbs increase to <color=#dbb536>10</color>;
Phase 2 Bond: Each stack of Orb Skill Extra DMG Bonus increases to <color=#dbb536>40%</color>, capped at <color=#dbb536>600%</color>;
Pinging Signal Orbs has a <color=#dbb536>80%</color> chance to generate an orb of the same color (including Special Orbs).
All <color=#dbb536>Phase 2</color> Bond effects will be inherited.
